Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼有去七辻屋的捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪裡有條像樣的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目那傢伙  都叫他跟緊點了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是給我走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就等他5秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這醜貓是…  記得是夏目家的貓貓老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很羞人的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你胖太算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪老師  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你是那個什麼田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個傻瓜還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  你還沒從夏目那裡聽說我的真實身份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪啊  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總體來說確實是的  不過我可是非常高貴的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我當成路邊的那種小妖混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還是頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次能和妖怪交談  這還是我的頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  你並不是能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏目才沒把我的事告訴你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你也幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏目的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目是我收的小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有給夏目帶來困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是你比較像小弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是你威脅了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  隨便你說話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了我的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要隱匿證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就開動了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓為什麼會和你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師就像是我的保鏢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  不想說的話也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為情況比較複雜  我也不知道該怎麼說明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…並不是想瞞著田沼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是想瞞著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想和田沼你能正常地交談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想讓你有不好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不好的回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看吧  我抓到大魚了  看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是祭典  今晚會舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  秋季廟會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去看看吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒準備完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在準備也沒關係  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等啦  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的話回去正好順路  我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  還沒好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都說了還在準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為至少會有路邊攤的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  還沒開始呢  有你的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為受人之託
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧…在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有？你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻嘛  我聽說這種熱鬧的地方最容易聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛  確實  有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純  抱歉  幫我把這些搬到前殿那去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  幫忙把那些搬到前殿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家拜託的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別頂撞班長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是一個班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你別去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人等一下就會幫你拿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下  我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的話  夏目一定也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然就是狐狸的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  竟然敢搗亂  你這小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是看不到我們的樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我都快準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  救救我  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太粗暴了點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係吧  給我閃邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到這狐狸弄翻的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡只有它在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是風大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙看得到我們啊  怪物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是空無一物到令人吃驚的地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天花板的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是池塘反射上去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院裡根本沒有池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得可能天花板上的水紋只有我們才能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼他看不到池塘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  被他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目家的醜貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子在我這的話  夏目就一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有沒有繩子  呀  越牢越好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  夏目  那不是鬍子  是肩胛骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得懂我的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  夏目也聽得懂我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來見那個人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  能見到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼謝謝你了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊  跟著它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能鎮靜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志他要直接去參加祭典的話告訴我們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  萬一遇到事故的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是愛擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了那種事  貓五郎會回來告訴我們的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志來我們家有多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是一直以來留下了太多不好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也太客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼隨便一點我也會輕鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此之間都那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不像一家人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得還是早了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  別人掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人掉落的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  先放在我這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個好像是別人掉的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  被抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  民子來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胖太？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我自言自語而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了  就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到呢  錢袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起在哪裡掉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有那麼重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊也找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你果然也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  貓咪老…不  有沒有看到我家的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻胖貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  我的迴轉燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  我剛才不是給你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒拿到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒拿到怎麼付你錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請問要多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面到底放了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我在一段時間內變成人類樣子的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是獸型的話  會給夏目添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼就由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被食物的香味引誘來的嗎  小狐狸  不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它跑進來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我把它拿到山上放生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的鍋煮沸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  我明明開的小火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子跑來人群裡可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  可是  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊  你在的話也就是說  名取先生他也在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  他和人有約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人拜託你跟著這孩子的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫無戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有人煙的地方和我這樣的存在交談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會被人忌諱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我是能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個爛好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…難道是剛才的小狐狸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位哥哥是好人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過夏目那傢伙  居然都不來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  醜貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近確實有點冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  不過很安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  夏目你是不是看到庭院裡的池塘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我只能看到天花板上的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐知道嗎  你能看到這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們很溫柔\N我覺得我說出來的話  他們一定會接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也因為他們很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會想到我一直以來的遭遇  為我心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣想可能很自私  我不想他們那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們可以一直微笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  比想像中還要棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為鄉下的話會更挫一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  其實我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個巨大的傢伙擋住我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的傢伙  妖怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但我能感覺到很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它都看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走一段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有夏目你也能看清楚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話可以看得清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些倒影裡的魚  其實是什麼顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊  忘恩負義的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著重要的保鏢不管  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的腳步聲漸漸接近的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:22:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這裡卻很溫暖
